attributeSource.infoString2: Better Homes and Gardens Mason Mcduffie Real Estate

data.description: Fall in love with simple, stunning living in this Lemmon Valley beauty! With spacious interiors and neutral finishes illuminated by plenty of natural light, this 2200 sq. ft home offers ample room for relaxing, entertaining, and day-to-day living. Enjoy a bright, open living area with a gas fireplace, backyard access, and practical layout that flows seamlessly into the kitchen, which features granite counters, a breakfast bar, and an abundance of both cabinetry and countertop space. In the primary suite, discover airy interiors and a bathroom with dual sinks, large soaking tub, and glass-enclosed shower. Other bedrooms provide abundant space for any lifestyle or purpose. Other practical, yet exciting features include a separate laundry room, sizable garage, ceiling fans in almost every room, sleek plank flooring and carpeting throughout, and a lovely fenced-in backyard with your own stamped patio, shaded by a beautiful wooden gazebo that you're sure to adore.  A delightful home in a desirable location... it doesn't get better than that!
